BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:466e84a8c41c709e26dc53f2b11c1ccc@mdh
DTSTAMP:20260630T131256Z
DTSTART:20260701T235000Z
DTEND:20260702T005000Z
SUMMARY:🏒 Stick & Puck – Sylvania\, OH
DESCRIPTION:<p>Dialed In Goaltending is focused on extending goaltenders opportunity to further life and hockey.</p>\n<p>Instructors with over a decade of instructing and coaching experience\, Dialed In Goaltending is taking charge of this forgotten position and teaching the valuable craft needed to succeed on and off the ice. The approach is aimed at developing technical and physical aspects needed to be a top-tier goaltender today. Continued learning of top puck-stoppers in today&rsquo\;s game accelerates our teaching. Properly conveying and implementing techniques develops the confidence of a Dialed In Goaltender.</p>\nThe clinics offered will supplement the engagement and reinforce the repetitions needed in developing technique and the effective base to continue succeeding.<br /><br />*NO REFUNDS/CREDITS\nRink: Tam-O-Shanter Ice Rink – Sylvania\, OH\n~58 mi from Ann Arbor\nPrice: $10\nSource: DaySmart\nInfo: https://apps.daysmartrecreation.com/dash/x/#/online/tamoshanter/event-registration\nConfirm with rink — schedule subject to change.
LOCATION:Tam-O-Shanter Ice Rink – Sylvania\, OH
URL:https://apps.daysmartrecreation.com/dash/x/#/online/tamoshanter/event-registration
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:f20232b669041b80bd851422ecdccda3@mdh
DTSTAMP:20260630T131256Z
DTSTART:20260702T160000Z
DTEND:20260702T172000Z
SUMMARY:🏒 Stick & Puck – Ann Arbor
